sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant Store (API)
    participant YottaPay Class
    participant YottaGate API

    Customer->>Store: Payment request (phone, amount)
    Store->>YottaPay: process($order, $data)
    YottaPay->>YottaGate: POST /login (get token)
    YottaGate-->>YottaPay: token
    YottaPay->>YottaGate: POST /onLinePayment (create adjustment)
    YottaGate-->>YottaPay: adjustment_id, transactionId
    YottaPay-->>Store: PaymentResult (success, adjustment_id)
    Store-->>Customer: Display OTP input form
    Customer->>Store: Submit OTP
    Store->>YottaPay: complete($order, ['otp' => '1234'])
    YottaPay->>YottaGate: PATCH /onLinePayment (confirm with OTP)
    YottaGate-->>YottaPay: completed=true, transactionId
    YottaPay-->>Store: PaymentResult (success)
    Store-->>Customer: Payment confirmation